TEXT.S: = Morocan = Gaga mniq Hwareyseyn Jweysweysyang ka alang Morocan. 161 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 389 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 66% niqan 256 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 34% niqan 133 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Amis58%, Tayal1%, Bunun5%, ni rahuq na o2%.
